      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner to take it on some fun trips! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin. I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
