    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical provenance is highlighted by a documented rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high-torque loads. The M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional power delivery out of corners, complemented by a suspension system recently refreshed with OEM-spec bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior displays minor road patina, the VANOS system has been overhauled to maintain peak volumetric efficiency, and the hydraulic steering rack remains precise and communicative. A mechanically honest build for the discerning purist.",
