      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 996.2 Carrera 2, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus technology. This naturally aspirated power plant is paired with a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle, delivering linear power to the rear wheels. The vehicle benefits from a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement, ensuring drivetrain longevity. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a multi-link rear suspension geometry that provides exceptional mechanical grip and communicative feedback. Equipped with four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors, the braking system offers consistent modulation and thermal resilience. This is a purist\u2019s specification, prioritizing visceral performance and engineering substance.",
